 are on track to hit 200+ properties by the end of the year. And each one i=
s unreal.=C2=A0
As you know, Wander isn=E2=80=99t your typical vacation rental. They combin=
e the quality of a luxury hotel with the comfort of a private vacation home=
=2E And they=E2=80=99ve added stunning fla=
gship locations like Wander Falling=
 Leaves [ https://substack.com/redirect/3d4d29d2-f0d9-483a-ab6d-8cfc8cf28fc=
0?j=3DeyJ1IjoiOXAwZ3QifQ.gb8J5T7GnA_ZlNuaMZjmlXXepKbqOsa8-6m8ExkRNpU ] in A=
ustin, Texas, Wander Oconee Shores [ https://substack.com/redirect/fd0f61be=
-f3e9-48f2-9d25-2a0ab9048949?j=3DeyJ1IjoiOXAwZ3QifQ.gb8J5T7GnA_ZlNuaMZjmlXX=
